hi Dmitriy,

The mentioned bug is reported in LP [1] and I have pushed a fix [2] for it.
As a workaround you can set swift_store_retry_get_count to 0 in the config
file.

Let me know if mentioned fix [2] works for you.

[1] https://bugs.launchpad.net/glance/+bug/2146432
[2] https://review.opendev.org/c/openstack/glance_store/+/982221

Thanks & Best Regards,

Abhishek Kekane


